column2: SELECT AlbumID, SUM(UnitPrice) AS totalPrice, COUNT(AlbumID)         AS numTracks     FROM chinook.Track      GROUP BY AlbumID ) SELECT TOP # album.Title AS &&&, artist.Name, f.totalPrice, f.numTracks FROM f JOIN chinook.Album album ON album.AlbumID=f.AlbumID JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON artist.ArtistID=album.ArtistID ORDER BY totalPrice DESC
